parse

private void parse(java.util.List<java.io.File> list)
            throws ParseException
Parses the source files. If it is defined in three step.
  • Step one: type information
  • Step two: atttributes, methods and local declarations, also import and extends
  • Step three: method body and instructions

    • Parameters:
    list - list of files
    Throws:
    ParseException - parse problem
    See Also:
    ASTParser, ASTParser.setCompilerOptions(Map), JavaCore, JavaCore.getDefaultOptions()
